creator: Nottingham City Council
descriptionHtml:
The Robin Hood Network is a partnership offering easy, accessible, smart travel across a network of bus, tram and train operators. The new Robin Hood app has everything you need to help you get around Nottingham.

Browse and tap on bus stops to explore upcoming departures, or check out the routes from a stop to see where you could travel next. Quickly save your favourite stops, timetables and regular journeys too.

Use our multi-modal journey planner to plan your trip throughout the Robin Hood Network. With complete timetables too, you can see times for every route at a glance.

You can send us your feedback via the app.
descriptionShort: The new Robin Hood app has everything you need to get around Nottingham.
